0.5.1
        * Changed the simualted_piecewise dataset and updated documentation
        * astsa package no longer imported
        * adaptspec examples included
        * intracranial_eeg dataset now a univariate time series
        * Updated authoring
        * 29.11.2016

0.5.0
        * Plots are now optional output for adaptspec (plotting = TRUE)
        * Updated documentation for adaptspec
        * Updated documentation for simulated_piecewise
        * Updated simulated_piecewise dataset
        * 25.11.2016

0.4.0
        * Added intracranial eeg dataset to adaptSPEC (intracranial_eeg)
        * Fixed bug in sourcing lin_basis_func
        * Fixed bug in sourcing beta_derivs
        * 01.11.2016

0.3.0
        * Changed package name from adaptSPEC to BayesSpec
        * Plots are now attributes on the adaptspec() function instead of being printed automatically
        * Updated descriptions
        * 13.10.2016

0.2.0
        * Added simulated_piecewise dataset
        * Removed exporting of adaptspec supporting functions
        * Included onAttach message
        * Fixed bug in dependent pacakge loadings
        * Added NEWS file
        * 05.10.2016

0.1.0
        * Initial internal development
        * adaptspec and supporting functions only
        * 29.09.2016
